{"tha-ap135:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap135:0.2":"Sobhitavagga ","tha-ap135:0.3":"3 Candanapujanakattheraapadana ","tha-ap135:1.1":"“Candabhaganaditire, ","tha-ap135:1.2":"ahosim kinnaro tada; ","tha-ap135:1.3":"Pupphabhakkho caham asim, ","tha-ap135:1.4":"pupphanivasano tatha. ","tha-ap135:2.1":"Atthadassi tu bhagava, ","tha-ap135:2.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap135:2.3":"Vipinaggena niyyasi, ","tha-ap135:2.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","tha-ap135:3.1":"Namo te purisajanna, ","tha-ap135:3.2":"cittam te suvisodhitam; ","tha-ap135:3.3":"Pasannamukhavannosi, ","tha-ap135:3.4":"vippasannamukhindriyo. ","tha-ap135:4.1":"Orohitvana akasa, ","tha-ap135:4.2":"bhuripanno sumedhaso; ","tha-ap135:4.3":"Sanghatim pattharitvana, ","tha-ap135:4.4":"pallankena upavisi. ","tha-ap135:5.1":"Vilinam candanadaya, ","tha-ap135:5.2":"agamasim jinantikam; ","tha-ap135:5.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap135:5.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap135:6.1":"Abhivadetvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap135:6.2":"lokajettham narasabham; ","tha-ap135:6.3":"Pamojjam janayitvana, ","tha-ap135:6.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap135:7.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap135:7.2":"candanam yam apujayim; ","tha-ap135:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap135:7.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap135:8.1":"Catuddase kappasate, ","tha-ap135:8.2":"ito asimsu te tayo; ","tha-ap135:8.3":"Rohani nama namena, ","tha-ap135:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap135:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap135:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap135:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap135:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma candanapujanako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap135:11.1":"Candanapujanakattherassapadanam tatiyam. ","tha-ap135:11.2":"Atthamabhanavaram. "}